## Red Flags to Avoid

Never do these without explicit justification:
- Ignoring existing design patterns "because it's outdated"
- Adding animations longer than 300ms
- Using more than 3 font families
- Implementing inaccessible color contrasts
- Creating non-responsive designs
- Using inline styles instead of proper CSS
- Copying Dribbble designs without adaptation

